values:
Man I wonder why I don't ever update this thing. Anyway, been looking into the whole law school deal. Pretty tough, gonna have to manage at least a B+ average as well as score high on the LSAT's. Trying to keep it in california, so Aiming for USC Law (which is the 28th hardest law school to get into...Cal 3rd, UCLA 7th, UCD, 38th) UCD by the way does have a law school and it's pretty good actually. 

But Aside from all that, thinking about majors, along the lines of Economics, or Sociology with Law and Society emphasis, Communications, or Economy, Justice, and Society (minor). Yeah, whatever, have to pick up the pace and shit to get all that done though.

On a side note, prolly gonna plan a trip down to LA/SD sometime between the last 2 weekends of April and the first weekend of May. I'll see how that all pans out.
fuck..i was so pissed off that I was just about to do the thing that I told myself I would never do...fuck it all

Yeah so it turns out that my girlfriend is suppose to be some horny nympho. Well I've been goin out with her for 9 months and I guess the whole world knew but me. Heh, shit, who the hell have I been dating. Anyway, enough with that.

So I'm betting on this weekends playoffs games. Titans to win and Eagles/Packers to score over 45 combined I think it was.

Yeah so Me, Charles, Alex, Joyin, Jimmy, Julia, Son, Jennifer, Kevin, Allison hmm forgot how many l's were in her name had a few shots and alcohol jello to ring in the new quarter. Heh well lets just say that was stupendous.

Yeah so Albert, token black guy #2 from our dorm is ranting about how he was in San Diego before Davis started and he ran into the Real World San Diego crew. Just so he could be on tv he was doin his black thing so this big white cracker on the show tryin to start a fight...well im a little trippy right now but the point is that episode will be aired this upcoming tuesday at 10:00 pm on MTV.

hi guys, i'm will! i'm a cool and tall guy. i'm especially cool now that i have a livejournal, thanx to my bud, heidi! i'm going to constantly update this for your amusement, my friends, so sit tight and enjoy! i'm currently at stevo's playing mariokart with fred, steve, and sun. i'm little princess and little bowzer (?) (dont worry, i dont always talk like this, heidi's making me sound queer on purpose) winterbreak's been jolly good fun, though it'll soon come to an end. for new years, i gambled with the guys at simon's all night long. i was up... but then... well dont worry about it. okay, he's playing games. the end for now. [btw, hi corinne ;) ] --written by hideelicious--
